OBJECT Report 78779 PCS Details
{
  OBJECT-PROPERTIES
  {
    Date=;
    Time=;
    Version List=4PS9.00.BK.OK;
  }
  PROPERTIES
  {
    CaptionML=ENU=PCS Details;
    OnPreReport=BEGIN
                  IF Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter") <> '' THEN
                    PeriodFilterTxt := Job.GETFILTER("Period Filter");
                END;

    OnPostReport=VAR
                   lvJobRec@1100409002 : Record 11072003;
                   AccPeriod@1100409001 : Record 50;
                   TempDate@1100409000 : Date;
                 BEGIN
                 END;

  }
  DATASET
  {
    { 1100409000;0;DataItem;JobTable         ;
               DataItemTable=Table11072003;
               OnPreDataItem=VAR
                               Permissions@1100409000 : Codeunit 11012026;
                             BEGIN
                               SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                               SETRANGE("Cumulation Filter", 0D, GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));

                               Permissions.CostControlReports(Job);

                               DPA_SetFilters(CurrReport.OBJECTID(FALSE));
                               CumulationFilterTxt := GETFILTER("Cumulation Filter");
                               EVALUATE(DatFilterEnd, STRSUBSTNO('%1',GETRANGEMAX("Cumulation Filter")));
                             END;

               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  DeterminePrognosisDate@1100409000 : Codeunit 11012029;
                                  PrevPrognosisRec@1100409001 : Record 11012034;
                                  SearchProgrDate@1100409002 : Codeunit 11012014;
                                  JobRec@1100409008 : Record 11072003;
                                  PostingRequired@1100409007 : Boolean;
                                  lPrognosisLine@1100409006 : Record 11012035;
                                  lActualCostLabor@1100409005 : Decimal;
                                  lPrognLabor@1100409004 : Decimal;
                                  lPrognOtherTypes@1100409003 : Decimal;
                                  PrevAllowedDec@1100409015 : Decimal;
                                  PrevAllowedHoursDec@1100409014 : Decimal;
                                  PurchaseDec@1100409013 : Decimal;
                                  EstimPurchResultDec@1100409012 : Decimal;
                                  PurchCostDec@1100409011 : Decimal;
                                  ActualPurchResultDec@1100409010 : Decimal;
                                  TotPurchResultDec@1100409009 : Decimal;
                                  Language@1000000000 : Record 8;
                                BEGIN
                                  CurrReport.LANGUAGE := Language.GetLanguageID("Language Code");
                                  ClearVariabels;

                                  SearchPrognosis("No.", FALSE);//JobTable."Single/Main/Sub Project" = JobTable."Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project");//todo
                                  SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date");

                                  CASE "Single/Main/Sub Project" OF
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project": ProjSrtTxt := STRSUBSTNO('%1 (incl. deelproject)',
                                      FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project"));
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project": ProjSrtTxt := FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                    "Single/Main/Sub Project"::Single: ProjSrtTxt := FORMAT("Single/Main/Sub Project");
                                  END;
                                  CALCFIELDS("Open (Purchase)","Received/Not Invoiced","Project Contract Amount",
                                             "Extension Contract Amount","Actual Costs",Prognosis,"Risc Coverage (Prognosis)");
                                  CALCFIELDS("Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Open (Inventory)", Revenues,"Actuals Period",
                                             "Actual Preclosure Result","Open Amount (Hours)", Budget);
                                  CALCFIELDS("Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)","Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)","Principal Name","Name Project Manager");

                                  JobRec.GET("No.");
                                  JobRec.COPYFILTERS(JobTable);
                                  JobRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                                  Job.GET(JobTable."No.");
                                  Job.COPYFILTERS(JobTable);

                                  IF DoublePrognType THEN
                                    WarningText := STRSUBSTNO(Warr001, PrognLevelTxt);

                                  TotCostDec[1] := CostContMgt.TotCostProject(Job,TRUE);
                                  PrognosisDec := PrognosisDec - TotCostDec[1];

                                  //Ophalen laatste produktiestand binnen periodefilter
                                  DetermPrognosisDate.DetermineBothDates(JobRec);       //ProgressFilter
                                  DetermineProductionDate.DetermineBothDates(JobRec);   //PrognosisFilter
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project" THEN
                                    SETFILTER("Project Filter","No.")
                                  ELSE
                                    SETFILTER("Project Filter",'');

                                  {IF NOT SplitMainProjects THEN BEGIN                     //uitsplitsen hoofdprojecten
                                    PrognResultDec := CostContMgt.PrognResultProject(JobRec,FALSE);
                                    IF PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed THEN
                                      PrognEndResultDec[1] := CostContMgt.PrognEndResultProject(JobRec,TRUE)
                                    ELSE
                                      PrognEndResultDec[1] := (PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues" - PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Cost") -
                                        (("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") - Budget);
                                    IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project" THEN BEGIN
                                      CalcPayedAndToPay("No.",'',RemainingDec,TotalInvoiced, TRUE);
                                      CalculateBudget(FALSE,"No.",Corr,BegrootMEMI);
                                    END ELSE BEGIN
                                      CalculateBudget(TRUE,"No.",Corr,BegrootMEMI);
                                      CalcPayedAndToPay("No.",'',RemainingDec,TotalInvoiced, FALSE);
                                    END;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN   }
                                    JobRec.SETRANGE("Main Project","No.");
                                    IF JobRec.FINDSET THEN
                                      REPEAT
                                        PrognResultDec += CostContMgt.PrognResultProject(JobRec,FALSE);
                                      IF PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed THEN
                                        PrognEndResultDec[1] += CostContMgt.PrognEndResultProject(JobRec,TRUE)
                                      ELSE
                                        PrognEndResultDec[1] := (("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") - Budget) -
                                          (PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues" - PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Cost");
                                  {
                                    IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project" THEN BEGIN
                                      CalcPayedAndToPay("No.",'',RemainingDec,TotalInvoiced, TRUE);
                                      CalculateBudget(FALSE,"No.",Corr,BegrootMEMI);
                                    END ELSE BEGIN
                                      CalculateBudget(TRUE,"No.",Corr,BegrootMEMI);
                                      CalcPayedAndToPay("No.",'',RemainingDec,TotalInvoiced, FALSE);
                                    END;     }
                                    //PrognEndResultDec[1] := PrognEndResultDec[1]  + (-Corr + BegrootMEMI);

                                        CalcPayedAndToPay(JobRec."No.",'',RemainingDec,TotalInvoiced,TRUE);
                                      UNTIL JobRec.NEXT = 0;
                                  //END;

                                  OriginalBudget := Budget;// - (Corr + BegrootMEMI);
                                  CALCFIELDS("Project Contract Amount");

                                  Perc1 := 0;
                                  Perc2 := 0;
                                  Perc3 := 0;
                                  Perc4 := 0;
                                  Perc5 := 0;
                                  Perc6 := 0;
                                  Perc7 := 0;
                                  DekkingTotaleKosten := 0;
                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project" THEN
                                    CalculateDekkingTotaleKosten("No.",TRUE)
                                  ELSE
                                    CalculateDekkingTotaleKosten("No.",FALSE);

                                  IF ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    Perc1 := "Actual Costs" / ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount");
                                    Perc2 := ("Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" +
                                              "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                              "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" + "Open (Inventory)" +
                                              "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)") /
                                             ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount");
                                    Perc3 := PrognosisDec / ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount");
                                    IF PrognTotRevenue[1] <> 0 THEN
                                      Perc4 := (PrognTotRevenue[1] - TotCostDec[1] - PrognosisDec) / PrognTotRevenue[1];
                                  END;

                                  IF "Actual Costs" <> 0 THEN
                                    Perc5 := (DekkingTotaleKosten / ("Actual Costs" + "Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)"
                                  +
                                             "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                             "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" + "Open (Inventory)" +
                                             "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)") /
                                             "Actual Costs");

                                  IF ErrCounter > 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    PostingRequired := FALSE;
                                    JobRec.GET("No.");
                                    IF JobRec."Posting Element Mandatory" THEN
                                      PostingRequired := TRUE;
                                    IF PostingRequired THEN
                                      MessageTxt := STRSUBSTNO(ErrorElementVerpl,ErrCounter)
                                    ELSE
                                      MessageTxt := STRSUBSTNO(ErrorElementNietVerpl,ErrCounter);
                                  END;

                                  //PrognEndResultDec[1] := CalcPrognEndResult("No.");

                                  //Uitrekenen percentages
                                  CLEAR(PercArr);
                                  IF "Project Contract Amount" <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    PercArr[1] := ROUND((("Project Contract Amount" - OriginalBudget) / "Project Contract Amount"),0.01);
                                    PercArr[2] := ROUND(((Corr / "Project Contract Amount")),1);
                                  END;
                                  IF "Extension Contract Amount" - MEMITLOpdr <> 0 THEN
                                    PercArr[3] := ((("Extension Contract Amount" - MEMITLOpdr) - ( BegrootMEMI - BegrootMEMITLOpdr)) / ("Extension Contract Amount" - MEMITLOpdr));
                                  IF ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    PercArr[4] := ROUND((("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount" - Budget) / ("Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount")),0.01);
                                    PercArr[5] := ROUND((PrognEndResultDec[8] / ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount")),0.01);
                                    PercArr[6] := ROUND(((("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") - Budget) + PrognEndResultDec[8]) /
                                                  ("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount"),0.01);
                                    IF MEMITLOpdr <> 0 THEN
                                      PercArr[8] := ROUND((MEMITLOpdr - BegrootMEMITLOpdr) / MEMITLOpdr,0.01);
                                  END;

                                  IF Budget <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETRANGE("Project No.", "No.");
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETRANGE("Cost Type", CostTypeControlRec."Cost Type"::Labor);
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETRANGE("Main Project No.", "Main Project");
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETRANGE("Project Filter", "No.");
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
                                    CostTypeControlRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                                    IF CostTypeControlRec.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
                                      CostTypeControlRec.CALCFIELDS("Actual Costs");
                                      lActualCostLabor := CostTypeControlRec."Actual Costs";
                                    END;
                                    lPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", "No.");
                                    lPrognosisLine.SETFILTER("Prognosis Date",'..%1',DatFilterEnd);
                                    lPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Cost Type", lPrognosisLine."Cost Type"::Labor);
                                    IF lPrognosisLine.FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
                                      lPrognosisLine.CALCFIELDS("Total Prognosis Labor");
                                      lPrognLabor := lPrognosisLine."Total Prognosis Labor";
                                    END;
                                    lPrognosisLine.RESET;    //Geprognosticeerde dekking
                                    lPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Project No.", "No.");
                                    lPrognosisLine.SETRANGE("Prognosis Date", PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date");
                                    IF lPrognosisLine.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                      REPEAT
                                        IF lPrognosisLine."Ovh. Surcharge" <> 0 THEN
                                          GeprognDekking := GeprognDekking + lPrognosisLine."Ovh. Surcharge";
                                      UNTIL lPrognosisLine.NEXT = 0;
                                    END;
                                  END;

                                  IF ("Actual Costs" + "Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" +
                                     "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                     "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" + "Open (Inventory)" +
                                     "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)") <> 0 THEN
                                       Perc6 := ((DekkingTotaleKosten + GeprognDekking) /
                                         ("Actual Costs" + "Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" +
                                         "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                         "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" + "Open (Inventory)" +
                                         "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)"));

                                  IF Prognosis <> 0 THEN
                                    PercArr[7] := ROUND((GeprognDekking / Prognosis),0.01);

                                  SETRANGE("Prognosis Filter", PrognosisDateF);

                                  IF "Single/Main/Sub Project" = "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Main Project" THEN
                                    ResultSubProjDec := CalcResultSubProject("No.");

                                  CalcCostCompRate(Job);
                                END;

               ReqFilterFields=No. }

    { 8   ;1   ;Column  ;COMPANYNAME         ;
               SourceExpr=COMPANYNAME }

               SourceExpr=GetReportName }

               SourceExpr=PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" }

    { 9   ;1   ;Column  ;ExtraDate_Job       ;
               SourceExpr=ExtraDate }

    { 1100409020;1;Column;ProjSrtTxt_Job     ;
               SourceExpr=ProjSrtTxt }

    { 1100409022;1;Column;ContractAmount_Job ;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Contract Amount" }

    { 1100409023;1;Column;OriginalBudget_Job ;
               SourceExpr=OriginalBudget }

    { 1100409024;1;Column;ContractAmountMinBudget_Job;
               SourceExpr="Project Contract Amount" - OriginalBudget }

    { 1100409025;1;Column;Corr_Job           ;
               SourceExpr=Corr }

    { 1100409026;1;Column;ExtensionContractAmountMinMEMITLOpdr_Job;
               SourceExpr="Extension Contract Amount" - MEMITLOpdr }

    { 1100409027;1;Column;BegrootMEMIMinBegrootMEMITLOpdr_Job;
               SourceExpr=BegrootMEMI - BegrootMEMITLOpdr }

    { 1100409028;1;Column;BegrootMemiTotaal_Job;
               SourceExpr=("Extension Contract Amount" - MEMITLOpdr) - ( BegrootMEMI - BegrootMEMITLOpdr) }

    { 1100409029;1;Column;MEMITLOpdr_Job     ;
               SourceExpr=MEMITLOpdr }

    { 1100409030;1;Column;BegrootMEMITLOpdr_Job;
               SourceExpr=BegrootMEMITLOpdr }

    { 1100409031;1;Column;MEMITLOpdrMinBegrootMEMITLOpdr_Job;
               SourceExpr=MEMITLOpdr - BegrootMEMITLOpdr }

    { 1100409032;1;Column;WarningPrognTxt_Job;
               SourceExpr=WarningPrognTxt }

    { 1100409033;1;Column;ExtensionContractAmount_Job;
               SourceExpr="Extension Contract Amount" }

    { 1100409034;1;Column;Budget_Job         ;
               SourceExpr=Budget }

    { 1100409035;1;Column;PrognEndResultDec1_Job;
               SourceExpr=PrognEndResultDec[1] }

    { 1100409036;1;Column;ResultSubProjDec_Job;
               SourceExpr=ResultSubProjDec }

    { 1100409037;1;Column;ActualPreclosureResult_Job;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Actual Preclosure Result" }

    { 1100409038;1;Column;ProvisionLossResult_Job;
               IncludeCaption=Yes;
               SourceExpr="Provision Loss Result" }

    { 1100409188;1;Column;ExpectFinResult_Job;
               SourceExpr=((PrognEndResultDec[1] + "Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") - Budget) - ResultSubProjDec - "Actual Preclosure Result" - "Provision Loss Result" }

    { 1100409039;1;Column;PrognTotRevenue1_Job;
               SourceExpr=PrognTotRevenue[1] }

    { 1100409040;1;Column;Obligations_Job    ;
               SourceExpr="Open (Purchase)" + "Received/Not Invoiced" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" + "Open Amount (Hours)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" + "Open (Inventory)" + "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + "Risc Coverage (Prognosis)" }

    { 1100409041;1;Column;Prognosisdec1_Job  ;
               SourceExpr=PrognosisDec }

    { 1100409042;1;Column;PrognResult_Job    ;
               SourceExpr=PrognTotRevenue[1] - TotCostDec[1] - PrognosisDec }

    { 1100409043;1;Column;DifnPrognResult_Job;
               SourceExpr=((("Project Contract Amount" + "Extension Contract Amount") - Budget) + PrognEndResultDec[1]) - (PrognTotRevenue[1] - TotCostDec[1] - PrognosisDec) }

    { 1100409044;1;Column;DekkingTotaleKosten_Job;
               SourceExpr=DekkingTotaleKosten }

    { 1100409045;1;Column;GeprognDekking_Job ;
               SourceExpr=GeprognDekking }

    { 1100409046;1;Column;VerwachteDekking_Job;
               SourceExpr=DekkingTotaleKosten + GeprognDekking }

    { 1100409047;1;Column;CostCompRate1_Job  ;
               SourceExpr=CostCompRate[1] }

    { 1100409048;1;Column;CostCompRate2_Job  ;
               SourceExpr=CostCompRate[2] }

    { 1100409049;1;Column;CostCompRate3_Job  ;
               SourceExpr=CostCompRate[3] }

    { 1100409061;1;Column;CostCompRate26_Job ;

    { 1100409065;1;Column;Revenues_Job       ;
               SourceExpr=Revenues }

    { 1100409189;1;Column;PercArr1_Job       ;

    { 1100409155;1;DataItem;                 ;
               DataItemTable=Table11012047;
               DataItemTableView=SORTING(Project No.,Cost Type,Cost Object);
               OnAfterGetRecord=VAR
                                  DeterminePrognosisDate@1100409015 : Codeunit 11012029;
                                  PrevPrognosisRec@1100409014 : Record 11012034;
                                  SearchProgrDate@1100409013 : Codeunit 11012014;
                                  JobRec@1100409012 : Record 11072003;
                                  PostingRequired@1100409011 : Boolean;
                                  lPrognosisLine@1100409010 : Record 11012035;
                                  lActualCostLabor@1100409009 : Decimal;
                                  lPrognLabor@1100409008 : Decimal;
                                  lPrognOtherTypes@1100409007 : Decimal;
                                  PrevAllowedDec@1100409006 : Decimal;
                                  PrevAllowedHoursDec@1100409005 : Decimal;
                                  PurchaseDec@1100409004 : Decimal;
                                  EstimPurchResultDec@1100409003 : Decimal;
                                  PurchCostDec@1100409002 : Decimal;
                                  ActualPurchResultDec@1100409001 : Decimal;
                                  TotPurchResultDec@1100409000 : Decimal;
                                BEGIN
                                  IF ElementBln THEN BEGIN
                                    CPECO.RESET;
                                    CPECO.SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.",Element,"Cost Type","Cost Object");
                                    CPECO.SETAUTOCALCFIELDS("Original Budget Amount",Adjustments,Extension,Budget,"Actual Costs","Prognosis Total Cost",
                                                            "Prognosis Previous Period","Open (Purchase)","Received/Not Invoiced","Open (Inventory)",
                                                            "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Risc Coverage","Risc Coverage (Prognosis)",
                                                            "Original Budget Hours","Adjustments Hours","Extension Hours","Budget Hours","Actual Hours");
                                    CPECO.SETRANGE("Project No.","Control Project/Cost Object"."Project No.");
                                    CPECO.SETRANGE("Cost Object","Control Project/Cost Object"."Cost Object");
                                    CPECO.SETRANGE("Cost Type","Control Project/Cost Object"."Cost Type");
                                    CPECO.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
                                    //CPECO.SETRANGE("Cumulation Filter", 0D, Job.GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));

                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(CPECO."Original Budget Amount",CPECO."Original Budget Hours",CPECO.Adjustments,CPECO."Adjustments Hours",CPECO.Extension,
                                      CPECO."Extension Hours",Budget,CPECO."Budget Hours", "Actual Costs",TotCostDec);
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(TotHoursDec,"Actuals Period",CPECO."Allowed Costs",CPECO."Allowed Hours",PrognTotCostDec[2],PrognTotHoursDec,
                                      PrognEndResultDec,AllowedDec,AllowedHoursDec);
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Open (Purchase)","Received/Not Invoiced","Open Amount (Hours)",
                                      "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Open (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Risc Coverage (Prognosis)");
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)","Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)");

                                    IF CPECO.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                      CPECO.CALCFIELDS(Description);
                                      ClearVarCostObj;

                                      CPECO.SETFILTER("Period Filter",PeriodFilterTxt);
                                      CPECO.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter",CumulationFilterTxt);
                                      CPECO.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date");

                                      CostContMgt.CalcFieldsElemCostObj(CPECO);
                                      CostContMgt.AllowedAndPurchElemCostObj(
                                        CPECO,
                                        AllowedDec, AllowedHoursDec, PrevAllowedDec, PrevAllowedHoursDec,
                                        PurchaseDec, EstimPurchResultDec, PurchCostDec, ActualPurchResultDec, TotPurchResultDec,TRUE);

                                      IF Budget <> 0 THEN
                                        AllowedPerc := AllowedDec / Budget * 100;   //is geen functie voor op dit niveau
                                      TotCostDec[2] := CostContMgt.TotCostElemCostObj(CPECO,FALSE);
                                      TotHoursDec := CostContMgt.TotHoursElemCostObj(CPECO,FALSE);
                                      PrognTotCostDec[2] := CostContMgt.PrognTotCostElemCostObj(CPECO,FALSE);
                                      IF CPECO."Cost Type" = CPECO."Cost Type"::Labor THEN
                                        PrognTotHoursDec := CostContMgt.PrognTotHoursElemCostObj(CPECO,FALSE);
                                      IF PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed THEN
                                        PrognEndResultDec[2] := CostContMgt.PrognEndResultElemCostObj(CPECO,FALSE);
                                      IF (PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed) AND
                                        (PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date" <> PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Date") THEN
                                        PrognEndResultDec[3] := CalcPrognEndResPrevPeriodElem(CPECO);

                                      COBJ_ELementField         := CPECO.Element;
                                      COBJ_CostTypeField        := STRSUBSTNO('%1',CPECO."Cost Type");
                                      COBJ_CostObjectField      := CPECO."Cost Object";
                                      COBJ_CostComponentField   := CPECO."Cost Component";
                                      COBJ_DescriptionField     := CPECO.Description;
                                      COBJ_OriginalBudgetAmount := CPECO."Original Budget Amount";
                                      COBJ_OriginalBudgetHours  := ROUND(CPECO."Original Budget Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Adjustments          := CPECO.Adjustments;
                                      COBJ_AdjustmentHours      := ROUND(CPECO."Adjustments Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Extension            := CPECO.Extension;
                                      COBJ_ExtensionHours       := ROUND(CPECO."Extension Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Budget               := CPECO.Budget;
                                      COBJ_BudgetHours          := ROUND(CPECO."Budget Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_ActualCost           := CPECO."Actual Costs";
                                      COBJ_Open                 := CPECO."Open (Purchase)" + CPECO."Received/Not Invoiced" + CPECO."Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                                                   CPECO."Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" + CPECO."Open Amount (Hours)" + CPECO."Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" +
                                                                   CPECO."Open (Inventory)" + CPECO."Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + CPECO."Risc Coverage (Prognosis)";
                                      COBJ_TotCostDec           := TotCostDec[2];
                                      COBJ_TotHoursDec          := TotHoursDec;
                                      COBJ_ActualsPeriod        := CPECO."Actuals Period";
                                      COBJ_AllowedDec           := AllowedDec;
                                      COBJ_AllowedHoursDec      := ROUND(AllowedHoursDec,0.1);
                                      COBJ_PrognTotCostDec      := PrognTotCostDec[2];
                                      COBJ_PrognTotHoursDec     := ROUND(PrognTotHoursDec,0.1);
                                      COBJ_PrognEndResult1      := PrognEndResultDec[1];
                                      COBJ_PrognEndResult2      := PrognEndResultDec[2];
                                      COBJ_PrognEndResult3      := PrognEndResultDec[3];
                                    END;
                                  END ELSE BEGIN
                                    CPCO.RESET;
                                    CPCO.SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.","Cost Type","Cost Object");
                                    CPCO.SETAUTOCALCFIELDS("Original Budget Amount",Adjustments,Extension,Budget,"Actual Costs","Prognosis Total Cost",
                                                           "Prognosis Previous Period","Open (Purchase)","Received/Not Invoiced","Open (Inventory)",
                                                           "Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Risc Coverage","Risc Coverage (Prognosis)",
                                                           "Original Budget Hours","Adjustments Hours","Extension Hours","Budget Hours","Actual Hours");

                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(CPCO."Original Budget Amount",CPCO."Original Budget Hours",CPCO.Adjustments,CPCO."Adjustments Hours",CPCO.Extension,
                                      CPCO."Extension Hours",CPCO.Budget,CPCO."Budget Hours", CPCO."Actual Costs",TotCostDec);
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS(TotHoursDec,"Actuals Period",CPCO."Allowed Costs",CPCO."Allowed Hours",PrognTotCostDec[2],PrognTotHoursDec,
                                      PrognEndResultDec,AllowedDec,AllowedHoursDec);
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Open (Purchase)","Received/Not Invoiced","Open Amount (Hours)",
                                      "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)","Open (Inventory)","Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)","Risc Coverage (Prognosis)");
                                    CurrReport.CREATETOTALS("Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)","Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)");

                                    CPCO.SETRANGE("Project No.","Control Project/Cost Object"."Project No.");
                                    CPCO.SETRANGE("Cost Object","Control Project/Cost Object"."Cost Object");
                                    CPCO.SETRANGE("Cost Type","Control Project/Cost Object"."Cost Type");
                                   // CPCO.SETRANGE("Cumulation Filter", 0D, Job.GETRANGEMAX("Period Filter"));
                                    IF CPCO.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
                                      CPCO.CALCFIELDS(Description);
                                      ClearVarCostObj;

                                      CPCO.SETFILTER("Period Filter",PeriodFilterTxt);
                                      CPCO.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter",CumulationFilterTxt);
                                      CPCO.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date");

                                      CostContMgt.CalcFieldsCostObj(CPCO);

                                      CostContMgt.AllowedAndPurchCostObj(
                                        CPCO,
                                        AllowedDec, AllowedHoursDec, PrevAllowedDec, PrevAllowedHoursDec,
                                        PurchaseDec, EstimPurchResultDec, PurchCostDec, ActualPurchResultDec, TotPurchResultDec,TRUE);

                                      AllowedPerc := CostContMgt.AllowedPercCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      TotCostDec[2] := CostContMgt.TotCostCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      TotHoursDec := CostContMgt.TotHoursCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      PrognTotCostDec[2] := CostContMgt.PrognTotCostCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      IF CPCO."Cost Type" = CPCO."Cost Type"::Labor THEN
                                        PrognTotHoursDec := CostContMgt.PrognTotHoursCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      IF PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed THEN
                                        PrognEndResultDec[2] := CostContMgt.PrognEndResultCostObj(CPCO,FALSE);
                                      IF (PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed) AND
                                        (PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date" <> PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Date") THEN
                                        PrognEndResultDec[3] := CalcPrognEndResPrevPeriod(CPCO);

                                      COBJ_ELementField         := '';
                                      COBJ_CostTypeField        := STRSUBSTNO('%1',CPCO."Cost Type");
                                      COBJ_CostObjectField      := CPCO."Cost Object";
                                      COBJ_CostComponentField   := CPCO."Cost Component";
                                      COBJ_DescriptionField     := CPCO.Description;
                                      COBJ_OriginalBudgetAmount := CPCO."Original Budget Amount";
                                      COBJ_OriginalBudgetHours  := ROUND(CPCO."Original Budget Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Adjustments          := CPCO.Adjustments;
                                      COBJ_AdjustmentHours      := ROUND(CPCO."Adjustments Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Extension            := CPCO.Extension;
                                      COBJ_ExtensionHours       := ROUND(CPCO."Extension Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_Budget               := CPCO.Budget;
                                      COBJ_BudgetHours          := ROUND(CPCO."Budget Hours",0.1);
                                      COBJ_ActualCost           := CPCO."Actual Costs";
                                      COBJ_Open                 := CPCO."Open (Purchase)" + CPCO."Received/Not Invoiced" + CPCO."Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" +
                                                                   CPCO."Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" + CPCO."Open Amount (Hours)" + CPCO."Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)" +
                                                                   CPCO."Open (Inventory)" + CPCO."Open Ovh. Surch. (Inventory)" + CPCO."Risc Coverage (Prognosis)";
                                      COBJ_TotCostDec           := TotCostDec[2];
                                      COBJ_TotHoursDec          := TotHoursDec;
                                      COBJ_ActualsPeriod        := CPCO."Actuals Period";
                                      COBJ_AllowedDec           := AllowedDec;
                                      COBJ_AllowedHoursDec      := ROUND(AllowedHoursDec,0.1);
                                      COBJ_PrognTotCostDec      := PrognTotCostDec[2];
                                      COBJ_PrognTotHoursDec     := ROUND(PrognTotHoursDec,0.1);
                                      COBJ_PrognEndResult2      := PrognEndResultDec[2];
                                      COBJ_PrognEndResult3      := PrognEndResultDec[3];

                                    END;
                                  END;
                                END;

               DataItemLink=Project No.=FIELD(No.),
                            Period Filter=FIELD(Period Filter),
                            Cumulation Filter=FIELD(Cumulation Filter),
                            Progress Filter=FIELD(Progress Filter),
                            PrevProgressFilter=FIELD(PrevProgressFilter),
                            Prognosis Filter=FIELD(Prognosis Filter) }

    { 1100409203;2;Column;COBJ_ElementField  ;
               SourceExpr=COBJ_ELementField }

    { 1100409156;2;Column;COBJ_CostTypeField ;
               SourceExpr=COBJ_CostTypeField }

    { 1100409066;2;Column;COBJ_CostObjectField;
               SourceExpr=COBJ_CostObjectField }

    { 1100409067;2;Column;COBJ_CostComponentField;

    { 1100409069;2;Column;COBJ_OriginalBudgetAmount;
               SourceExpr=COBJ_OriginalBudgetAmount }

    { 1100409070;2;Column;COBJ_OriginalBudgetHours;
               SourceExpr=COBJ_OriginalBudgetHours }

    { 1100409071;2;Column;COBJ_Adjustments   ;

      ActualTotCostDec@1100409015 : Decimal;

      BudgetDec@1100409013 : ARRAY [50] OF Decimal;
      BudgetHour@1100409012 : ARRAY [50] OF Decimal;
      CostCompRate@1100409011 : ARRAY [50] OF Decimal;
      TotCost@1100409010 : ARRAY [50] OF Decimal;
      TotHour@1100409009 : ARRAY [50] OF Decimal;
      ResultSubProjDec@1100409008 : Decimal;
      WarningPrognTxt@1100409007 : Text[100];
      InclSubProjBln@1100409006 : Boolean;
      ElementBln@1100409005 : Boolean;
      Counter@1100409004 : Integer;
      PrognLevelTxt@1100409003 : Text[50];
      ProjSrtTxt@1100409002 : Text[50];
      WarningText@1100409001 : Text[250];
      DoublePrognType@1100409000 : Boolean;
      COBJ_ELementField@1100409100 : Text[50];
      COBJ_CostTypeField@1100409099 : Text[50];
      COBJ_CostObjectField@1100409068 : Text[30];
      COBJ_CostComponentField@1100409069 : Text[30];
      COBJ_DescriptionField@1100409070 : Text[50];
      COBJ_OriginalBudgetAmount@1100409071 : Decimal;
      COBJ_OriginalBudgetHours@1100409072 : Decimal;
      COBJ_Adjustments@1100409073 : Decimal;
      COBJ_AdjustmentHours@1100409097 : Decimal;
      COBJ_Extension@1100409074 : Decimal;
      COBJ_ExtensionHours@1100409075 : Decimal;
      COBJ_Budget@1100409076 : Decimal;
      COBJ_BudgetHours@1100409077 : Decimal;

      COBJ_Open@1100409079 : Decimal;

      "-----------------"@1100409092 : TextConst;

      CPCO@1100409095 : Record 11012047;
      CPECO@1100409096 : Record 11012050;
      ExtraDate@1000 : Date;

    PROCEDURE CalculateBudget@1000000030(MainBool@1000000000 : Boolean;JobNo@1000000001 : Code[20];VAR CorrBudget@1000000002 : Decimal;VAR ExtBudget@1000000003 : Decimal);
    VAR
      BudgetLine@1000000004 : Record 11012001;
      JobRec@1000000005 : Record 11072003;
      ExtensionContract@1000000006 : Record 11012004;
    BEGIN
      //MainBool                      TRUE: Alleen hoofproject              FALSE: Hoofd en deelprojecten
      IF NOT MainBool THEN BEGIN
        BudgetLine.SETRANGE("Project No.",JobNo);
        BudgetLine.SETFILTER(Adjustment,'<>%1','');
        IF BudgetLine.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          BudgetLine.CALCSUMS(Amount);
          CorrBudget := BudgetLine.Amount;
        END;
        BudgetLine.SETRANGE(Adjustment);
        BudgetLine.SETFILTER("Extension Contract",'<>%1','');
        IF BudgetLine.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            CASE BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status" OF
              BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status"::Order:ExtBudget += BudgetLine.Amount;
              BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status"::"Invoicing Allowed":ExtBudget += BudgetLine.Amount;
            END;
          UNTIL BudgetLine.NEXT = 0;
        END;
        ExtensionContract.RESET;
        ExtensionContract.SETRANGE("Project No.",JobNo);
        ExtensionContract.SETFILTER("Version Date",CumulationFilterTxt);
        ExtensionContract.SETRANGE("Treat like Order", TRUE);
        IF ExtensionContract.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
          REPEAT
            IF (ExtensionContract.Status = ExtensionContract.Status::Offered) OR
              (ExtensionContract.Status = ExtensionContract.Status::Applied) THEN BEGIN
                MEMITLOpdr := MEMITLOpdr + ExtensionContract."Expected Contract Amount";
                ExtensionContract.CALCFIELDS(Budget);
                BegrootMEMITLOpdr := BegrootMEMITLOpdr + ExtensionContract.Budget;
              END;
          UNTIL ExtensionContract.NEXT = 0;
        END;
      END ELSE BEGIN
        JobRec.SETRANGE("Main Project", JobNo);
        IF JobRec.FINDSET THEN
          REPEAT
            BudgetLine.RESET;
            BudgetLine.SETRANGE("Project No.",JobRec."No.");
            BudgetLine.SETFILTER(Adjustment,'<>%1','');
            IF BudgetLine.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
              BudgetLine.CALCSUMS(Amount);
              CorrBudget := ExtBudget + BudgetLine.Amount;
            END;
            BudgetLine.SETFILTER(Adjustment,'%1','');
            BudgetLine.SETFILTER("Extension Contract",'<>%1','');
            IF BudgetLine.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
              REPEAT
                CASE BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status" OF  //NVT|(>=Opdracht&<Vervallen)
                  BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status"::"Not Applicable":ExtBudget += BudgetLine.Amount;
                  BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status"::Order:ExtBudget += BudgetLine.Amount;
                  BudgetLine."Extension Contract Status"::"Invoicing Allowed":ExtBudget += BudgetLine.Amount;
                END;
              UNTIL BudgetLine.NEXT = 0;
            END;
            ExtensionContract.RESET;
            ExtensionContract.SETRANGE("Project No.",JobRec."No.");
            ExtensionContract.SETFILTER("Version Date",CumulationFilterTxt);
            ExtensionContract.SETRANGE(Status, ExtensionContract.Status::Offered);
            ExtensionContract.SETRANGE("Treat like Order", TRUE);
            IF ExtensionContract.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
              REPEAT
                MEMITLOpdr := MEMITLOpdr + ExtensionContract."Expected Contract Amount";
                ExtensionContract.CALCFIELDS(Budget);
                BegrootMEMITLOpdr := BegrootMEMITLOpdr + ExtensionContract.Budget;
              UNTIL ExtensionContract.NEXT = 0;
            END;
          UNTIL JobRec.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE ClearVariabels@1000000054();
    BEGIN
      CLEAR(BegrootMEMI);
      CLEAR(Corr);
      CLEAR(OriginalBudget);
      TotCostDec[1] := 0;
      PrognTotCostDec[2] := 0;
      CLEAR(PrognResultDec);
      CLEAR(PrognEndResultDec);
      CLEAR(PrognTotRevenue);
      CLEAR(PrognosisDec);
      CLEAR(GeprognDekking);
      CLEAR(GrprognFinResultDec);
      CLEAR(CostCompRate);
      CLEAR(ResultSubProjDec);
      CLEAR(ProjSrtTxt);
      CLEAR(PrognLevelTxt);
    END;

    PROCEDURE ClearVarCostObj@1000000029();
    BEGIN
      TotCostDec[2] := 0;
      CLEAR(TotHoursDec);
      //CLEAR(PrognEndResultDec);
      //CLEAR(PrognTotHoursDec);
      CLEAR(AllowedDec);
      CLEAR(AllowedHoursDec);
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalculateDekkingTotaleKosten@1000000021(JobNo@1000000000 : Code[20];SubProj@1000000002 : Boolean);
    VAR
      JobLedgerEntry@1000000001 : Record 11072005;
    BEGIN
      JobLedgerEntry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Cost Type","Entry Type","Posting Date","Purchase Action");

      IF SubProj THEN
        JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Job No.",JobNo)
      ELSE
        JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Main Project No.",JobNo);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Posting Date",0D,DatFilterEnd);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE("Entry Type",JobLedgerEntry."Entry Type"::Usage);
      JobLedgerEntry.SETRANGE(Surcharge,TRUE);
      IF JobLedgerEntry.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          DekkingTotaleKosten := DekkingTotaleKosten + JobLedgerEntry."Total Cost (LCY)";
        UNTIL JobLedgerEntry.NEXT = 0;
      END;

      DekkingTotaleKosten := DekkingTotaleKosten + + Job."Open Ovh. Surch. Soft (Purch.)" + Job."Open Ovh. Surch. Firm (Purch.)" + Job.
      "Open Ovh. Surch. (Hours)";
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcPayedAndToPay@1000000064(JobNo@1000000003 : Code[20];ExtContr@1000000012 : Code[20];VAR RemainingAmnt@1000000007 : Decimal;VAR TotalFact@1000000008 : Decimal;DeelProj@1000000014 : Boolean);
    VAR
      jobledgentry@1000000000 : Record 11072005;
      custledgentry@1000000001 : Record 21;
      SalesInvoiceHeader@1000000002 : Record 112;
      SalesCrMemoHeader@1000000006 : Record 114;
      TempInvoiceNo@1000000004 : Code[20];
      Perc@1000000005 : Decimal;
      PostCounter@1000000009 : Integer;
      DaysOfDue@1000000010 : Integer;
      DueAmnt@1000000011 : Decimal;
      PeilDatum@1000000013 : Date;
    BEGIN
      jobledgentry.SETCURRENTKEY("Job No.","Posting Date");

      PeilDatum := DatFilterEnd;
      IF DeelProj THEN
        jobledgentry.SETRANGE("Job No.",JobNo)
      ELSE
        jobledgentry.SETRANGE("Main Project No.",JobNo);
      IF ExtContr <> '' THEN
        jobledgentry.SETRANGE("Extension Contract",ExtContr);
      jobledgentry.SETFILTER("Posting Date",CumulationFilterTxt);
      jobledgentry.SETRANGE("Entry Type",jobledgentry."Entry Type"::Sale);
      IF jobledgentry.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          IF jobledgentry."Document No." <> TempInvoiceNo THEN BEGIN
            custledgentry.SETRANGE("Document No.",jobledgentry."Document No.");
            custledgentry.SETRANGE("Customer No.",jobledgentry.Principal);
            IF custledgentry.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
              Perc := 0;
              //Verkoopfactuur
              IF SalesInvoiceHeader.GET(jobledgentry."Document No.") THEN BEGIN
                SalesInvoiceHeader.CALCFIELDS("Amount VAT",Amount);
                Perc := 0;
                IF (SalesInvoiceHeader."Amount VAT" <> 0) THEN
                  Perc := ROUND(100 / (SalesInvoiceHeader.Amount / SalesInvoiceHeader."Amount VAT"),1);
                TotalFact := TotalFact + SalesInvoiceHeader.Amount;
              END;
              //Creditnota's
              IF SalesCrMemoHeader.GET(jobledgentry."Document No.") THEN BEGIN
                SalesCrMemoHeader.CALCFIELDS("Amount VAT",Amount);
                Perc := 0;
                IF (SalesCrMemoHeader."Amount VAT" <> 0) THEN
                  Perc := 100 / (SalesCrMemoHeader.Amount / SalesCrMemoHeader."Amount VAT");
                  TotalFact := TotalFact + SalesCrMemoHeader.Amount;
              END;

              custledgentry.CALCFIELDS("Original Amt. (LCY)","Remaining Amt. (LCY)");
              IF Perc <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                RemainingAmnt := RemainingAmnt + ((custledgentry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)") / ((Perc/100) + 1));
                PostCounter := PostCounter + 1;
                IF custledgentry."Due Date" < PeilDatum THEN BEGIN
                  DaysOfDue := DaysOfDue + (PeilDatum - custledgentry."Due Date");
                  DueAmnt := DueAmnt + ((custledgentry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)") / ((Perc/100) + 1));
                END;
              END ELSE BEGIN
                RemainingAmnt := RemainingAmnt + ((custledgentry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)"));
                PostCounter := PostCounter + 1;
                IF custledgentry."Due Date" < PeilDatum THEN BEGIN
                  DaysOfDue := DaysOfDue + (PeilDatum - custledgentry."Due Date");
                  DueAmnt := DueAmnt + custledgentry."Remaining Amt. (LCY)";
                END;
              END;

            END;
          END;
          TempInvoiceNo := jobledgentry."Document No.";
        UNTIL jobledgentry.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcPrognEndResPrevPeriod@1000000010(pRec@1000000000 : Record 11012047) : Decimal;
    VAR
      lvPeriodType@1000000006 : 'Day,Week,Month,Quarter,Year,Accounting Period';
      lvPeriodFilterTxt@1000000005 : Text[30];
      lvCumulationFilterTxt@1000000004 : Text[30];
      lvDatFilterStart@1000000003 : Date;
      lvDatFilterEnd@1000000002 : Date;
      lvPeriodNo@1000000001 : Text[1024];
      lvContrlCostObjRec@1000000007 : Record 11012047;
      DecArray@1210190000 : ARRAY [10] OF Decimal;
    BEGIN
      lvDatFilterStart := DatFilterStart;
      lvDatFilterEnd := DatFilterEnd;
      lvCumulationFilterTxt := CumulationFilterTxt;
      lvPeriodFilterTxt := PeriodFilterTxt;

      SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,
        PeriodType::"Accounting Period",'<=');
      //MESSAGE(STRSUBSTNO('%1 %2',lvCumulationFilterTxt,PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Date"));
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Project No.", Job."No.");
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", lvCumulationFilterTxt);
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", lvPeriodFilterTxt);
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Date");
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Cost Type", pRec."Cost Type");
      lvContrlCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Cost Object", pRec."Cost Object");
      IF lvContrlCostObjRec.FINDFIRST THEN
        CostContMgt.CalcFieldsCostObj(lvContrlCostObjRec);

      EXIT(CostContMgt.PrognEndResultCostObj(lvContrlCostObjRec,TRUE));
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcPrognEndResPrevPeriodElem@1000000059(pRec@1000000000 : Record 11012050) : Decimal;
    VAR
      lvPeriodType@1000000006 : 'Day,Week,Month,Quarter,Year,Accounting Period';
      lvPeriodFilterTxt@1000000005 : Text[30];
      lvCumulationFilterTxt@1000000004 : Text[30];
      lvDatFilterStart@1000000003 : Date;
      lvDatFilterEnd@1000000002 : Date;
      lvPeriodNo@1000000001 : Text[1024];
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec@1000000007 : Record 11012050;
      DecArray@1210190000 : ARRAY [10] OF Decimal;
    BEGIN
      lvDatFilterStart := DatFilterStart;
      lvDatFilterEnd := DatFilterEnd;
      lvCumulationFilterTxt := CumulationFilterTxt;
      lvPeriodFilterTxt := PeriodFilterTxt;

      SearchPeriod.FindPeriod(lvDatFilterStart,lvDatFilterEnd,lvCumulationFilterTxt,lvPeriodFilterTxt,
        PeriodType::"Accounting Period",'<=');

      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Project No.", Job."No.");
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", lvCumulationFilterTxt);
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Period Filter", lvPeriodFilterTxt);
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Date");
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETRANGE(Element, pRec.Element);
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Cost Type", pRec."Cost Type");
      lvContrlElemCostObjRec.SETRANGE("Cost Object", pRec."Cost Object");
      IF lvContrlElemCostObjRec.FINDFIRST THEN
        CostContMgt.CalcFieldsElemCostObj(lvContrlElemCostObjRec);

      EXIT(CostContMgt.PrognEndResultElemCostObj(lvContrlElemCostObjRec,TRUE));
    END;

    PROCEDURE SearchPrognosis@1000000001(pJobNo@1000000000 : Code[20];MainProject@1000000002 : Boolean);
    VAR
      lvAccPeriod@1000000001 : ARRAY [2] OF Record 50;
      lvJob@1000000003 : Record 11072003;
    BEGIN
      CLEAR(PrognosisRec);

      IF MainProject THEN BEGIN
        lvJob.RESET;
        lvJob.SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project");
        lvJob.SETRANGE("Main Project", pJobNo);
      END ELSE BEGIN
        lvJob.SETRANGE("No.", pJobNo);
      END;

      IF lvJob.FINDFIRST THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          PrognosisRec[1].SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.", "Prognosis Date");
          PrognosisRec[1].SETRANGE("Project No.", lvJob."No.");
          PrognosisRec[1].SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", '<=%1', DatFilterEnd);
          //PrognosisRec[1].SETFILTER("Prognosis Date",  PeriodFilterTxt);
          IF PrognosisRec[1].FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
            PrognosisRec[1].CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Revenue","Prognosis Total Cost");
            CASE PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" OF
              PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Rough :
                BEGIN
                  IF PrognLevelTxt = '' THEN
                    PrognLevelTxt := FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level")
                  ELSE BEGIN
                    IF PrognLevelTxt <> FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level") THEN BEGIN
                      PrognLevelTxt := PrognLevelTxt + '-' + FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level");
                      DoublePrognType := TRUE;
                    END;
                  END;
                  PrognosisDec += PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Cost";   //Elders wordt PrognosisDec nog aangepast!
                  PrognTotCostDec[1] += PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Cost";
                  PrognTotRevenue[1] += PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues";
                  PrognFinRes += (PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues" - PrognosisRec[1]."Rough Prognosis Total Cost");
                END;
              PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed :
                BEGIN
                  IF PrognLevelTxt <>'' THEN BEGIN
                    IF PrognLevelTxt <> FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level") THEN BEGIN
                      PrognLevelTxt := PrognLevelTxt + '-' + FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level");
                      DoublePrognType := TRUE;
                    END;
                  END ELSE
                    PrognLevelTxt := FORMAT(PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level");
                  PrognosisDec += PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Total Cost";   //Elders wordt PrognosisDec nog aangepast!
                  PrognTotCostDec[1] += PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Total Cost";
                  PrognTotRevenue[1] += PrognosisRec[1]."Project Invoiced" + PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Revenue";
                  PrognFinRes += (PrognosisRec[1]."Project Invoiced" + PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Revenue" -
                    PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Total Cost");
                END;
            END;
          END;

          lvAccPeriod[1].SETFILTER("Starting Date",'<%1', DatFilterEnd);
          IF lvAccPeriod[1].FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
            PrognosisRec[2].SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.", "Prognosis Date");
            PrognosisRec[2].SETRANGE("Project No.", lvJob."No.");
            PrognosisRec[2].SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", '<=%1', lvAccPeriod[1]."Starting Date");
            IF PrognosisRec[2].FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
              PrognosisRec[2].CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Revenue");
              CASE PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level" OF
                PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level"::Rough : PrognTotRevenue[2] += PrognosisRec[2]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues";
                PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed: PrognTotRevenue[2] += PrognosisRec[2]."Project Invoiced" +
                  PrognosisRec[2]."Prognosis Revenue";
              END;
            END;
          END;

          lvAccPeriod[2].SETFILTER("Starting Date",'<%1', lvAccPeriod[1]."Starting Date");
          IF lvAccPeriod[2].FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
            PrognosisRec[3].SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.", "Prognosis Date");
            PrognosisRec[3].SETRANGE("Project No.", lvJob."No.");
            PrognosisRec[3].SETFILTER("Prognosis Date", '<=%1', lvAccPeriod[2]."Starting Date");

            IF PrognosisRec[3].FINDLAST THEN BEGIN
              PrognosisRec[3].CALCFIELDS("Prognosis Revenue");
              ExtraDate := PrognosisRec[3]."Prognosis Date";
              CASE PrognosisRec[3]."Prognosis Level" OF
                PrognosisRec[3]."Prognosis Level"::Rough : PrognTotRevenue[3] += PrognosisRec[3]."Rough Prognosis Total Revenues";
                PrognosisRec[3]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed: PrognTotRevenue[3] += PrognosisRec[3]."Project Invoiced" +
                  PrognosisRec[3]."Prognosis Revenue";
              END;
            END;
          END;
        UNTIL lvJob.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcCostCompRate@1000000000(lvJobRec@1000000000 : Record 11072003);
    VAR
      lvContrProjCostObj@1000000001 : Record 11012047;
    BEGIN
      WITH lvContrProjCostObj DO BEGIN
        SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.","Cost Component","Cost Object");
        SETRANGE("Project No.", lvJobRec."No.");
        SETFILTER("Cost Component",'<>%1','');
        lvJobRec.COPYFILTER("Cumulation Filter", "Cumulation Filter");
        lvJobRec.COPYFILTER("Period Filter", "Period Filter");
        lvJobRec.COPYFILTER("Progress Filter", "Progress Filter");
        lvJobRec.COPYFILTER("Prognosis Filter", "Prognosis Filter");
        IF FINDFIRST THEN
          REPEAT
            CostContMgt.CalcFieldsCostObj(lvContrProjCostObj);

            TotCostDec[2] := CostContMgt.TotCostCostObj(lvContrProjCostObj,FALSE);
            TotHoursDec := CostContMgt.TotHoursCostObj(lvContrProjCostObj,FALSE);

            IF "Cost Component" <> '' THEN BEGIN
              IF "Budget Hours" <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                CASE "Cost Component" OF
                  'CONS'  : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[1] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[1] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'ENG'   : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[2] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[2] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'IND'   : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[3] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[3] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'LEERL' : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[4] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[4] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'MONT'  : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[5] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[5] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'PPL'   : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[6] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[6] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'PRA'   : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[7] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[7] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'UITV'  : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[8] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[8] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                  'WVB'   : BEGIN
                              BudgetDec[9] += Budget;
                              BudgetHour[9] += "Budget Hours";
                            END;
                END;
              END;
              IF TotHoursDec <> 0 THEN BEGIN
                CASE "Cost Component" OF
                  'CONS'  : BEGIN
                              TotCost[20] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[20] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'ENG'   : BEGIN
                              TotCost[21] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[21] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'IND'   : BEGIN
                              TotCost[22] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[22] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'LEERL' : BEGIN
                              TotCost[23] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[23] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'MONT'  : BEGIN
                              TotCost[24] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[24] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'PPL'   : BEGIN
                              TotCost[25] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[25] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'PRA'   : BEGIN
                              TotCost[26] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[26] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'UITV'  : BEGIN
                              TotCost[27] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[27] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                  'WVB'   : BEGIN
                              TotCost[28] += TotCostDec[2];
                              TotHour[28] += TotHoursDec;
                            END;
                END;
              END;
            END;
          UNTIL NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcResultSubProject@1000000005(lvJobNo@1000000000 : Code[20]) : Decimal;
    VAR
      lvJobRec@1000000001 : Record 11072003;
      lvDec@1000000002 : Decimal;
    BEGIN
      WITH lvJobRec DO BEGIN
        SETCURRENTKEY("Main Project");
        SETRANGE("Single/Main/Sub Project", "Single/Main/Sub Project"::"Sub Project");
        SETRANGE("Main Project", lvJobNo);
        SETRANGE("Project Status", "Project Status"::Finished);
        IF FINDFIRST THEN
          CALCFIELDS("Closed Costs", "Closed Revenues");
          REPEAT
            lvDec += ("Closed Revenues" - -"Closed Costs");
          UNTIL NEXT = 0;
        EXIT(lvDec);
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE CalcPrognEndResult@1000000002(JobNo@1000000000 : Code[20]) PrognEndRes : Decimal;
    VAR
      CostControl@1000000001 : Record 11012047;
    BEGIN
      CostControl.SETCURRENTKEY("Project No.","Cost Type","Cost Object");
      CostControl.SETRANGE("Project No.", JobNo);
      CostControl.SETFILTER("Period Filter", PeriodFilterTxt);
      CostControl.SETFILTER("Cumulation Filter", CumulationFilterTxt);
      CostControl.SETFILTER("Prognosis Filter",'%1',PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Date");
      IF CostControl.FINDSET THEN BEGIN
        REPEAT
          IF PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level" = PrognosisRec[1]."Prognosis Level"::Detailed THEN
            PrognEndRes += CostContMgt.PrognEndResultCostObj(CostControl, TRUE);
        UNTIL CostControl.NEXT = 0;
      END;
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetReportName@1100525003() : Text;
    BEGIN
      EXIT(DELSTR(CurrReport.OBJECTID, 1, STRPOS(CurrReport.OBJECTID, ' ')));
    END;

    PROCEDURE GetReportFilter@1100525000() : Text;
    VAR
      postedhourlines@1000 : Record 11012085;
    BEGIN
      IF Job.GETFILTERS <> '' THEN
        EXIT(STRSUBSTNO('%1: %2', Job.TABLECAPTION, Job.GETFILTERS));
                   {
      //wegschrijven header
      //wegschrijven a t/md  met fill()
      wagecomponents.reset;
      if wagecomponents.findset then begin
        repeat
          fill(wagecomponents.CODE)
        until wagecomponents.next = 0;
      end;

      //nu heb je de header op naar de regels
      employee.reset
      if employee.findset then begin
        repeat
          wagecomponents.reset;
          if wagecomponents.findset then begin
            repeat
              postedhourline.setfilter(employee);
              postedhourline.setfilter(wagecomp);
              IF postedhourline.findset then begin
                fill(a t/m d obv employee) ;
                postedhourline.CALCSUMS(je veld);
                col+=1;
                fill(je veld) ;
              end;
            until wagecomponents.next=0;
          end;
        until employee.next=0;
      end;

           }
    END;

    BEGIN
    END.
  }

  <Code>Public Function BlankZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value = 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankZeroAndPos(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &gt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNeg(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt; 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function

Public Function BlankNegAndZero(ByVal Value As Decimal)
    if Value &lt;= 0 then
        Return ""
    end if
    Return Value
End Function
</Code>
